{
  "chapter": 95,
  "chapter_summary": "赵雅来找董匡询问项少龙消息，得知项少龙出现在邯郸附近后悲痛欲绝。赵雅求董匡带她追赶被拒，扑入怀中痛哭。项少龙以飞针作证物安抚赵雅，赵雅请求与他欢好。事后赵雅凭项少龙忘记涂香粉和体味识破其董匡身份，悲喜交集。项少龙承认心软弱点，原谅赵雅过往。赵雅发誓不再背叛，项少龙要求她助其取得城守之位。赵雅答应后离去。善柔责怪项少龙又与赵雅鬼混，陪他练剑。滕翼回府，项少龙与他商议破坏六国合纵之势，怀疑田单李园合谋偷袭，计划探访龙阳君打听消息。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_guo",
      "speaker_name": "乌果",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "雅夫人来了，我想请她到东轩等你，她却坚持要到内堂去，她的脸色很难看呢！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_guo",
      "text": "柔夫人和致姑娘呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_guo",
      "speaker_name": "乌果",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "她们回家去探望正叔，今晚不会回来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_guo",
      "text": "她们有没有碰上头？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_guo",
      "speaker_name": "乌果",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "柔夫人亲自接待她，致姑娘则躲了起来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "你的脸色为何如此难看？",
      "tone": "关心",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "董匡！你究竟有没有派人拦截项少龙？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "夫人何出此言，我董匡难道是轻诺寡信的人吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "那为何我们接到消息，项少龙扮作行脚商人出现在邯郸东面三十里的一条小村庄，还与当地的守军发生激战呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "有没有捉到项少龙？",
      "tone": "关心",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "荒山野岭，谁能拿得住他？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "既是如此，那夫人的脸色为何这般难看？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我也不知道，或者是怕他知道自己行藏败露，再不会到邯郸来。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "其实前天晚上我的手下便截住他，还告诉他我们是奉夫人之命去警告他，至于他为何仍会来到离邯郸这么近的地方，就非我所能明白，我刚刚收到这消息，故未能通知夫人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你不是骗我吧？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "你在这里稍候片刻，我去拿证物给你过目，然后再把你轰出府门，永远不再见你。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "天啊！你们真的找到少龙，他……他有什么话说？",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "他什么话也没有说，只是当我的人问他要证物，他由挂满飞针的腰囊挑一根出来，接着离开。想不到现仍未走，确有胆识。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "董匡你可否再为赵雅做一件事？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "什么事呢？嘿！我差点忘了要把你轰走，你还厚颜来求我做这做那。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "立即带我去赶上他好吗？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "这怎可能呢！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "夫人前世定是欠了那项少龙很多眼泪，所以今世要还个够本。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "根本没有人可代替项少龙在你心中的位置，夫人不要再骗自己和我老董了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我想试试看，董匡，现在我很需要男人，可否抱赵雅到房里去？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你还犹豫什么呢？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "董郎为何还不上来？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "这几天李园还有来找夫人吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "在这时候，还要提起其他人吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "先答我的问题。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "答案是没有，近几天我避到宫内去，什么人都没有见，心中只有两个人，一个是董马痴，另一个你也知是谁。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "李园在榻上比之项少龙如何？",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不要问这种令人难堪的问题好吗？噢……",
      "tone": "苦恼",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "我想知道！",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "没有人及得上项少龙，他是天生最懂爱惜女人的男人，啊！董匡！求你不要再折磨赵雅，好吗？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我真的很开心，开心得纵然立刻死了也无悔！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "我比之项少龙又如何？",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你是指以前的项少龙吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "夫人何出此言？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙你不用骗我了！今天你忘记涂上香粉，身上的药味又不浓重，人家刚才伏在你怀里，把你认出来，所以要和你合体交欢，好作证实，唉！少龙啊！你虽有通天本领，在榻上又怎瞒得过人家呢？天啊！世上竟有这么精美的面具，骗得雅儿苦透了。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "田单批评得好，我项少龙最大的弱点就是心软，见到你为我那样凄凉无助、不顾一切的样儿，早抛开往事，否则你怎能投怀送抱，拆穿我的西洋镜？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "什么西洋镜？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "总之是给你拆穿了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "天啊！你真的原谅雅儿了吗？少龙！求你吻吻人家啊！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙！唤我的名字好吗？雅儿自从干了对不起你的蠢事后，从没有一刻快乐过，苦透惨透哩！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "雅儿知错了，由今晚此刻开始，假若赵雅还敢做出任何背叛项少龙的行为，教赵雅受尽人间惨刑而亡。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "雅儿！雅儿！",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你真了得，只凭百多人便以迅雷不及掩耳的手法杀死乐乘，弄得我们疑神疑鬼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "你们曾怀疑过我吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "当然有啦！不过你的手下次晨精神抖擞地离城，没有半个受伤的人，使我们疑心尽释，唉！谁人斗得过你呢？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "人家可求你一件事吗？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "你是否又要和我做交易？",
      "tone": "不悦",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不！雅儿不敢，只是求你。",
      "tone": "惶恐",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "说吧！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "求你不要再用这种语气和人家说话好吗？那会使雅儿害怕你再次舍弃我。当日雅儿肯答应王兄来对付你，是有个不可以伤害你的协议，否则雅儿宁死也不会出卖你的。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "你还未说出要求。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "妮夫人之死实是赵穆一手造成，王兄事后非常内疚，但米已成炊，那亦是他疏远赵穆的主因。自乌家和你到秦国之后，他整个人像苍老十多年，且病痛缠身，老天早在折磨他了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "他似乎忘掉自己的女儿。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你不肯放过他吗？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "好吧！看在你份上，我不再和他计较。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙你真好，下命令吧！你要人家为你干什么都可以。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "助我取得城守之位。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "事不宜迟，现在雅儿立刻去见王兄，城守之位可包在我身上。唯一会反对的人是郭开，他早有心中的人选。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_guo",
      "speaker_name": "乌果",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "纪才女刚到，嘿！三爷真厉害，换了我便应付不来。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "看你成什么样子，睡极也不够，少管你一晚也不成。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "昨晚若有你在，我想爬起来都不行呢！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你不守承诺，又与赵雅鬼混，人家恨死你。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "乌果告诉你的吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "他敢不说吗？赵雅跟着还有纪嫣然，也不顾自己的身体。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "柔柔陪我去练剑好吗？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你的练功方法从哪里学来的？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "你的妹子呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "回武士行馆去了，她是教头来的嘛！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_shi_zi_mei",
      "speaker_name": "田氏姊妹",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "董爷终于醒了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我早预估到有此情况，三弟人又心软，对这荡女更是余情未了。不过这事对我们有百利无一害，让她将功赎罪好了。但你最好要赵大密切监视她，一有不妥，我们立即逃走。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_teng_yi",
      "text": "既有赵雅之助，我们索性大干一场，首先要破坏六国今天的合纵之势，说不定可以趁机狠狠挫折一下田单和李园。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你不是对田单有点好感吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_teng_yi",
      "text": "初时我还肯定偷袭我们的人是信陵君，现在愈想愈不像，极可能真是李园和田单合谋干出来的好事，意图破坏三晋合一。待会儿我去探访龙阳君，打听他的口气。唉！我很易便会信任人和为人所惑呢！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这是你的优点，也是缺点。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    }
  ],
